He looks like a dragon,

00:00:11.677 --> 00:00:13.113
and he starts swinging
the joystick

00:00:13.113 --> 00:00:15.414
in front of his body
like a martial arts weapon,

00:00:15.414 --> 00:00:18.450
and for the first time I saw
fear in my big brother's eyes.

00:00:18.450 --> 00:00:19.919
He was like, "Hey, dude,
take it easy,"

00:00:19.919 --> 00:00:23.556
and he's like--
[high-pitched voice] "Hiyah!"

00:00:23.556 --> 00:00:25.558
- The baby's coming!
